Omnistudio Data Mappers

A Data Mapper Turbo Extract retrieves data from a single Salesforce object type, with support for fields from related objects. You can filter the data and select the fields to return.

To create a Data Mapper Turbo Extract, specify its name, input and output types, and permissions.
Configure an Omnistudio Data Mapper Turbo Extract by specifying the object type, filters, fields to extract, and options.
Related Object Fields in Omnistudio Data Mapper Turbo Extracts allow you to select specific fields in related objects.
Test an Omnistudio Data Mapper Turbo Extract on the Preview tab.

A Data Mapper Turbo Extract has two advantages over a standard Data Mapper Extract: Simpler configuration and Better performance at runtime.
